snippet.title: This Is Snooker - Pool Deluxe Edition | Announcement Trailer [ENG]
snippet.description: Welcome to This Is Snooker – Pool Deluxe Edition, a genre-defining cue sports simulation featuring seven-time world snooker champion, Stephen Hendry. Coming soon to PS4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and Windows PC, from the creators of Pure Pool and Hustle Kings. Twitter: @VooFoo #ThisIsSnooker #ThisIsPool
